Class CombatArchetypes

java.lang.Object
game.combat.CombatArchetypes
Direct Known Subclasses:
Astrologer, Bandit, Samurai, Wretch
public abstract class CombatArchetypes extends Object
CombatArchetypes is an abstract class which provides the basic implementation of the starting class chosen by player.
